              </svg>
            </div>
            <blockquote class="slide-blockquote slide-blockquote-small" data-i18n="slide11-quote">
              "The same guardrails that protect you FROM rogue agents now need to protect the world FROM your intentionally hostile agents."
            </blockquote>
          </div>
          <div class="guardrail-rules">
            <div class="failure-card" data-delay="0">
              <h3 data-i18n="slide11-rule1-title">Isolate & Authorize</h3>
              <p class="failure-desc" data-i18n="slide11-rule1-desc">Sandbox your pentesting agents. Get written permission. Scanning production isn't testing — it's an incident.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="failure-card" data-delay="1">
              <h3 data-i18n="slide11-rule2-title">Verify Everything</h3>
              <p class="failure-desc" data-i18n="slide11-rule2-desc">Agents hallucinate vulnerabilities. Every finding needs human eyes before it becomes an action item.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

